d:
I never knew how rare it was to own these pages. They were not sold outside Japan, and even today you cant buy them online. I got them when I was in Japan.

I did not know how to get a printer to do this. So I took these with my phone its not perfect but better than nothing.

This shows some of the early pregnancy.

I have this theory that eventually, after he does more of the mothers backstories, there will be a new big story with all of them with a big pregnancy belly together.

We already saw a glimpse of this at the end of the second story.

https://e-hentai.org/s/9342743061/3558519-63

Kaede is clearly the woman on the right in that pic.
